      • on

        public void on(org.spongepowered.api.event.game.state.GameStartedServerEvent event)
        Sponge Listener method, registers the MagiBridge JDA instance as soon as it is available.

        Sometimes MagiBridge takes a while to start, if this is the case we register a delayed task to execute this method again 30 seconds later.

        Parameters:
        event - The event
